    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Periodical\" title=\"Periodical\">Periodical</a> * Computer Chess Reports</b>\n</p><p><b>Computer Chess Reports</b> (<b>CCR</b>),<br />\nan American computer chess periodical published quarterly from 1985 until 1996 by <i>Computer Chess Digest Incorporated</i> associated with <a href=\"/index.php?title=ICD_Corporation&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ICD Corporation (page does not exist)\">ICD Corporation</a>, as successor of the annual <b>Computer Chess Digest</b>, released in 1983 and 1984. Computer Chess Digest was primary edited by <a href=\"/Enrique_Irazoqui\" title=\"Enrique Irazoqui\">Enrique Irazoqui</a>, CCR by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Sostack&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Robert Sostack (page does not exist)\">Robert Sostack</a> and from 1987 by <a href=\"/Larry_Kaufman\" title=\"Larry Kaufman\">Larry Kaufman</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selected_Authors\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Authors</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Computer_Chess_Reports&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Quote from <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rec.games.chess.computer</a> FAQ: <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>:\n</p>\n<pre>Computer Chess Reports published quarterly by <a href=\"/index.php?title=ICD_Corporation&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ICD Corporation (page does not exist)\">ICD Corporation</a>, 21 Walt Whitman Road, Huntington Station, NY 11746.  Phone 800-645-4710.  Subscriptions are $18/year.  Focuses on computer chess, and rates <a href=\"/Dedicated_Chess_Computers\" title=\"Dedicated Chess Computers\">dedicated chess-playing computers</a> and software. This is worth looking at. \n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Authors\">Selected Authors</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Computer_Chess_Reports&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Authors\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Ingo_Alth%C3%B6fer\" title=\"Ingo Althöfer\">Ingo Althöfer</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Claudio_Bollini\" title=\"Claudio Bollini\">Claudio Bollini</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ivan_Bratko\" title=\"Ivan Bratko\">Ivan Bratko</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Joost_Buijs\" title=\"Joost Buijs\">Joost Buijs</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Michael_Byrne\" title=\"Michael Byrne\">Michael Byrne</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Truman_Collins\" title=\"Truman Collins\">Truman Collins</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Steven_Edwards\" title=\"Steven Edwards\">Steven Edwards</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Peter_Gillgasch\" title=\"Peter Gillgasch\">Peter Gillgasch</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Eric_Hallsworth\" title=\"Eric Hallsworth\">Eric Hallsworth</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Paul_Hsieh\" title=\"Paul Hsieh\">Paul Hsieh</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Robert Hyatt</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Enrique_Irazoqui\" title=\"Enrique Irazoqui\">Enrique Irazoqui</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Larry_Kaufman\" title=\"Larry Kaufman\">Larry Kaufman</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/David_Kittinger\" title=\"David Kittinger\">David Kittinger</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Danny_Kopec\" title=\"Danny Kopec\">Danny Kopec</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Richard_Lang\" title=\"Richard Lang\">Richard Lang</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mark_Lefler\" title=\"Mark Lefler\">Mark Lefler</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Fabian_M%C3%A4ser\" title=\"Fabian Mäser\">Fabian Maeser</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bruce_Moreland\" title=\"Bruce Moreland\">Bruce Moreland</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Thomas_Nitsche\" title=\"Thomas Nitsche\">Thomas Nitsche</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Walter_Ravenek\" title=\"Walter Ravenek\">Walter Ravenek</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Nick_Schoonmaker&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Nick Schoonmaker (page does not exist)\">Nick Schoonmaker</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schroder</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Brian_Sheppard\" title=\"Brian Sheppard\">Brian Sheppard</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Sam_Sloan\" title=\"Sam Sloan\">Sam Sloan</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Sostack&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Robert Sostack (page does not exist)\">Robert Sostack</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Kathe_Spracklen\" title=\"Kathe Spracklen\">Kathe Spracklen</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mark_Sturman\" title=\"Mark Sturman\">Mark Sturman</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mark_Uniacke\" title=\"Mark Uniacke\">Mark Uniacke</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jouni_Uski\" title=\"Jouni Uski\">Jouni Uski</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chris_Whittington\" title=\"Chris Whittington\">Chris Whittington</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bruce_Wright\" title=\"Bruce Wright\">Bruce C. Wright</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Computer_Chess_Reports&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/CCR_One_Hour_Test\" title=\"CCR One Hour Test\">CCR One Hour Test</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Kaufman_Test\" title=\"Kaufman Test\">Kaufman Test</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Computer_Chess_Reports&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess/kGruDcISu7M/IQHDGrpXaxoJ\">A Thank You From Computer Chess Reports</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Schwartz\" title=\"Steven Schwartz\">Steven Schwartz</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rec.games.chess</a>, June 05, 1995</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Computer_Chess_Reports&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesscomputeruk.com/html/computer_chess_digest.html\">Computer Chess Digest</a> hosted by <a href=\"/Mike_Watters\" title=\"Mike Watters\">Mike Watters</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesscomputeruk.com/html/computer_chess_reports.html\">Computer Chess Reports</a> hosted by <a href=\"/Mike_Watters\" title=\"Mike Watters\">Mike Watters</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Computer_Chess_Reports&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.faqs.org/faqs/games/chess/computer/part1/\">rec.games.chess.compute FAQ (1/3)</a> covers IDC's Computer Chess Reports</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Periodical\" title=\"Periodical\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228171808\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 41/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 78/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:1381-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228171808 and revision id 15567\n -->\n"
